'''比爾·赫默'''（Bill Hemmer，{{bd|1964年|11月14日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位記者，現在服務於[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞頻道]]，擔任America's Newsroom東岸時間上午9點至11點時段的主播。在此之前他曾在1995至2005年期間在[[CNN|CNN]]服務<ref name="cincygentlemen.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.cincygentlemen.com/hemmer.aspx |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2008-06-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210103045/http://www.cincygentlemen.com/hemmer.aspx |archivedate=2009-02-10 |df= }}</ref>。

==生平==
他出生在[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[辛辛那提|辛辛那提]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.americanprofile.com/article/4718.html |title=CNN's Bill Hemmer |publisher=''[[American_Profile|American Profile]]'' |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080210082918/http://www.americanprofile.com/article/4718.html |archivedate=2008-02-10 |df= }}</ref>，是一位羅馬天主教信徒<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cincygentlemen.com/hemmer.aspx |title=Bill Hemmer: The Journey Continues |publisher="CincyGentlemen.online" |year=2008 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210103045/http://www.cincygentlemen.com/hemmer.aspx |archivedate=February 10, 2009 }}</ref><ref name=justcause>{{cite web|url=http://justcauseit.com/articles/just-chatting-bill-hemmer |title=Just Chatting: Bill Hemmer |publisher=Just Cause |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091127082410/http://justcauseit.com/articles/just-chatting-bill-hemmer |archivedate=November 27, 2009 }}</ref>。赫默在大學期間曾經在當地的廣播電台出任DJ<ref name="nymag.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nymag.com/nymag/features/n_9548/index1.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417033315/http://nymag.com/nymag/features/n_9548/index1.html |archive-date=2015-04-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

